query:
SELECT cd.id, cd.customer_id, cd.document_type, cd.file_name, cd.analysis, cd.created_at 
FROM customer_documents cd 
JOIN customers c ON cd.customer_id = c.id 
WHERE c.name LIKE '%Fayyaz%' AND cd.document_type = 'switchboard_photo' 
ORDER BY cd.created_at DESC LIMIT 5;
